### =============================================
### SHOPEE - Diagnóstico e Testes
### =============================================

@token = SEU_JWT_TOKEN_AQUI
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### 1. Testar credenciais (sempre rodar primeiro)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/shopee/test-credentials
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 2. Buscar produto por itemId (máquina de lavar Colormaq)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/shopee/item/20599662745
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 3. Pesquisar por keyword
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/shopee/search?q=maquina+de+lavar
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 4. Gerar shortlink de afiliado
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/shopee/short-link
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://shopee.com.br/M%C3%A1quina-de-Lavar-Colormaq-12kg-i.781250043.20599662745"
}

###

### 5. Fluxo completo: URL → API Shopee → shortlink → banco
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/from-urls
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": "UUID_DA_CATEGORIA_AQUI",
  "urls": [
    "https://shopee.com.br/M%C3%A1quina-de-Lavar-Colormaq-12kg-i.781250043.20599662745"
  ]
}
